287
00:13:11,667 --> 00:13:12,709
De acuerdo.

288
00:13:12,793 --> 00:13:14,461
Y--

289
00:13:14,545 --> 00:13:17,714
Me gustas tanto que antes
de seguir adelante, solo quiero--

290
00:13:17,798 --> 00:13:19,591
